title: About
text: Welcome to the R users meetup group at Dedan Kimathi University of Technology! We are an R User group based in Dedan Kimathi University Of Technology in Nyeri, Kenya. We share knowledge about doing data science and machine learning with R through our weekly meetups every thuRsday where we learn, grow, and network together on everything Rstats.
